*Srećom* je sve dobro završilo. (Fortunately, everything ended well.)

Svi smo bili *srećni* što je sve završilo dobro. (We were all happy that everything ended well.)

Iznenada se desilo i *srećom* niko nije povređen. (It happened suddenly and luckily no one was injured.)

*Srećno* nam je sve prošlo. (We were lucky that everything went well.)

Mnogo nam je *sreće* trebalo da dođemo do ovde. (We needed a lot of luck to get here.)